nt and all the products mentioned may not be suited for you but you'll get a general sense of products that may work. For now, I'll just go over a few&nbsp;products, guidelines, and a general routine.</p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711459356644" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1711459356644"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Keep It SIMPLE!</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1711459356710" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459356710"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Sometimes the right way to start is to just take a moment and press the brakes on loading up on all the products on your wish list (don't worry that snail essence isn't going anywhere) and if you're feeling overwhelmed by all the unbelievably gorgeous skincare products out there, then it's okay to take a breather and keep it simple. Sticking to 3 basic steps and building up from there is perfectly fine. You should always feel comfortable with the products you are buying and feel confident about your skin decisions. Let's take a moment and go through these 3 simple steps together.</p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711459356713" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1711459356713"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Welcome to the 3 Basic Steps in a Sensitive Skin Care Routine</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1711459356660" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459356660"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><strong>Step 1: Water Based Cleanser.</strong></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Used to clean your face before applying your next steps.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><strong>Step 2: Moisturiser</strong></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Used to provide hydration and calm skin.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"><strong>Step 3: Sunblock</strong></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">Absorbs or reflects some of the sun UV rays, which provides protection to your skin.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;"></span></p><p><br></p><p>Remember we are taking baby steps here, you have to learn how to crawl before you take those 10 steps. Some great beginner sensitive skin products are:</p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" id="e-1711459356761" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1711459356761" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/0770018b-b54e-4fd4-a014-ff5870ce2131/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Desktop-Banner-Sensitive-Skin-Photos-Step1.jpg" alt="Step 1: Water Based Cleansers." class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" title="" data-width="60%" data-height="auto" width="1750" height="1062" natural-width="1750" natural-height="1062"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1711459356650" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1711459356650"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Step 1: Water Based Cleanser</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1711459356682" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1711459356682" style=""><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 383.333px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 191.667px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scrollElement" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 383px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="189" height="121" style="display: none; top: 3px !important; left: 0px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><div><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(24, 189, 134);"><a href="/products/innisfree-blueberry-rebalancing-5-5-cleanser" class="" style="" data-position="1">Innisfree - Blueberry Rebalancing 5.5 Cleanser</a></span><br style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif;">One of the most underrated cleansers, it has a pleasant Citrus scent, and is a gentle, thick, creamy cleanser. A small amount goes a long way. Great for dry/normal skin.</span><br></div><div><br></div><b><a href="/products/heimish-all-clean-green-foam" class="" style="color: rgb(24, 189, 134);" data-position="2">Heimish - All Green Foam</a></b><br><p>A lightly scented gel cleanser, that does not foam so much. PH of 5.5; a gentle cleanser best suited for oily/acne prone skin.<a href="/products/defence-barrier-ph-cleanser" class="" data-position="3"><br><span style="color: rgb(24, 189, 134);"><br><b>Purito - Defence Barrier Ph Cleanser</b></span></a><br>A gentle gel cleanser that won’t dry you out, great for combination skin. Has a stronger scent, and contains Tea Tree.<a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/innisfree-blueberry-rebalancing-5-5-cleanser" class="" data-position="4"><br></a><a href="/products/etude-house-soon-jung-whip-cleanser" class="" data-position="5"><br><b style="color: rgb(24, 189, 134);">Etude - Soon Jung Whip Cleanser</b></a><br></p><p>A gentle fragrance free light foam cleanser. Great for acne prone/normal/dry skin.<br></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1711459356669" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1711459356669" data-layout-lg="3+3+3+3" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+3+3+3" data-layout-sm="6+6+6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12+12+12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1669887786830" data-id="1669887786830"><div data-label="Product" data-key="product" data-atomgroup="product" id="m-1711459356609" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-product" data-ver="3.1" data-id="1711459356609" style="min-height: auto;" data-assigned-ver="4"><div class="module" data-variant="auto" style="" data-current-variant="39724040880257">{% assign p